headline: 2 Large Regional Bank Stocks That Could Get Acquired During the Trump Administration
summary: Mergers and acquisitions (M&A) could pick up in the banking sector under the Trump administration, which plans to deregulate the sector.  Large regional banks could experience consolidation.  The large regional players need to scale if they want to compete with the likes of JPMorgan Chase and Bank of America.
